evidence.text: None | 2025-06-30 | MINUTE ORDER: The Court GRANTS the parties' 29 Joint Motion for Briefing Schedule and sets the following deadlines. The current answer deadline of June 30, 2025, is VACATED. Plaintiffs' amended complaint is due by July 21, 2025. Defendants' motion to dismiss is due by September 18, 2025. Plaintiffs' opposition is due by October 9, 2025. Defendants' reply is due by October 30, 2025. SO ORDERED. Signed by Judge Trevor N. McFadden on 6/30/2025.
